videos.description: Virginia Tech's Ahmed Hill starts the game off hot as he sinks his third 3-pointer of the half against Washington.
videos.headline: Hill drills third 3-pointer for Hokies

videos.description: After scrambling for the loose ball, Justin Robinson finds Ahmed Hill behind the arch for an open 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Hokies' hustle leads to open 3 for Hill

videos.description: Hokies' P.J. Horne swings the ball to Justin Bibbs at the top of the arc for a 3-pointer in the first half.
videos.headline: Horne finds Bibbs for long ball

videos.description: Nickeil Alexander-Walker extends Virginia Tech's lead with a tough 3-point shot in the corner.
videos.headline: Alexander-Walker extends Hokies lead with contested three

videos.description: Washington's Jaylen Nowell finds Dan Kingma open in the corner for an uncontested 3-pointer in the second half.
videos.headline: Kingma drills 3-pointer off inbound

videos.description: Virginia Tech's Wabissa Bede sends a no-look pass to Justin Bibbs in the corner for a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Bibbs notches 30th point off no-look pass
